SwiftChat is a chat room based messenger available for all Android and iOS devices. With SwiftChat, everyone in the world can connect on all the most popular topics for free. SwiftChat uses your 3G or WiFi to browse, join, create chat rooms and message other users.

WHY SWIFTCHAT:

* COMPLETELY FREE: No fees, no hidden costs and no strings attached! Once downloaded you can send unlimited chat messages in any room to anyone, while meeting old friends and making new ones.
* DEVICE SECURED ACCOUNTS: No password or registration required, and no account details to remember! Choose your favorite user name and start sending instant messages right away.
* GLOBAL CHAT: Experience the unlimited freedom of sharing and socializing with people from all over the world. SwiftChat is not restricted by language, cultural or geographical barriers.
* HOTTEST TOPICS: Browse and engage in all the hottest, trending topics. SwiftChat aggregates all worldwide chat rooms and displays the rooms in simple, intuitive lists, ranked by popularity.
* UPVOTE: Upvote users and collect upvotes to unlock profile images, emoticons, stickers and other features.
* PHOTOS AND DRAWINGS: Take, upload, share and download photos with fellow users! Also use SwiftChat's drawing tools to share your own paintings, sketches, creations and show your artistic side!
* VIDEOS AND WEBSITES: Use SwiftChat's internet and video browsers to search for, view and share website links and videos - no need to exit SwiftChat!
* PROFILE: Customize your user profile for the world to see!
* GROUP CHAT: Enjoy live chat with groups of up to 100 like minded individuals. The more the merrier!
* CUSTOM ROOMS: Create custom chat rooms for others to join. Ask questions or start discussions as you desire
